sentence: We have acted as counsel to Oncothyreon Inc., a Delaware corporation (the Company), in connection with the registration of the resale, from time to time, of up to 5,150,680 shares (the Shares) of the Company s common stock, $ 0.0001 par value per share (the Common Stock), issued or issuable to the selling stockholder (the Selling Stockholder) named in the prospectus that forms a part of the Company s Registration Statement on Form S-3 filed on the date hereof (the Registration Statement).
